//TEXT
<jaT0001>October 17, 2046. It was exactly one year since that incident occurred. I had arrived too early, so I stood on the overlook gazing off into the distance.
<enT0001>October 17, 2046. It was exactly one year since that incident occurred. I had arrived too early, so I stood on the overlook gazing off into the distance.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>Today, memorial services were being held all across the country, but I came to participate in the military-sponsored ceremony being held here, at this airport.
<enT0002>Today, memorial services were being held all across the country, but I came to participate in the military-sponsored ceremony being held here, at this airport.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0003>"(We disobeyed orders in order to return, but now they're treating us like heroes... It was ridiculous.)"
<enT0003>"(We disobeyed orders in order to return, but now they're treating us like heroes... It was ridiculous.)"

//TEXT
<jaT0004>It seems there was a portion of the military who believed we should be strictly punished, but they were too afraid of public outcry to carry through.
<enT0004>It seems there was a portion of the military who believed we should be strictly punished, but they were too afraid of public outcry to carry through.

//TEXT
<jaT0005>Of course, it seems they were also afraid that certain facts they wanted to remain classified might be revealed if they held a court martial.
<enT0005>Of course, it seems they were also afraid that certain facts they wanted to remain classified might be revealed if they held a court martial.

//TEXT
<jaT0006>For example, I'm sure they wanted to hide the fact that the upper brass, who was "ruthless towards terrorists" according to the media, actually accepted their demands.
<enT0006>For example, I'm sure they wanted to hide the fact that the upper brass, who was "ruthless towards terrorists" according to the media, actually accepted their demands.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0007>"(Still... It's been a whole year since then...)"
<enT0007>"(Still... It's been a whole year since then...)"

//TEXT
<jaT0008>I looked up at the sky and let my emotions run. After we returned to Earth, every day passed by so fast it was hard to believe that a year had gone by.
<enT0008>I looked up at the sky and let my emotions run. After we returned to Earth, every day passed by so fast it was hard to believe that a year had gone by.

//TEXT
<jaT0009>We were hounded the press for a long time. Only recently was I able to live a normal life again...
<enT0009>We were hounded the press for a long time. Only recently was I able to live a normal life again...

//TEXT
<jaT0010>...Oh, I'm running out of time.
<enT0010>...Oh, I'm running out of time.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>I looked at my watch and realized it was almost time for me to meet up with her so I entered the airport and headed for our meeting spot.
<enT0011>I looked at my watch and realized it was almost time for me to meet up with her so I entered the airport and headed for our meeting spot.

//TEXT
<jaT0012>......
<enT0012>......

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0013>"Hey, Yu-san."
<enT0013>"Hey, Yu-san."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0014>"Ryota, you're five minutes late. What were you doing?"
<enT0014>"Ryota, you're five minutes late. What were you doing?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0015>"I, I'm sorry. I arrived here early, but I lost track of time when I started thinking outside..."
<enT0015>"I, I'm sorry. I arrived here early, but I lost track of time when I started thinking outside..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0016>"Oh well... I guess I'll overlook it this time. I'm not narrow minded enough to be mad about that."
<enT0016>"Oh well... I guess I'll overlook it this time. I'm not narrow minded enough to be mad about that."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0017>"Ohh, why thank ye very much..."
<enT0017>"Ohh, why thank ye very much..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0018>"Hehe... What is that?"
<enT0018>"Hehe... What is that?"

//TEXT
<jaT0019>Yu-san wore a bright smile. In this past year, she's started smiling a lot more often...
<enT0019>Yu-san wore a bright smile. In this past year, she's started smiling a lot more often...

//TEXT
<jaT0020>Besides, this wasn't the first time Yu-san and I had waited to meet each other.
<enT0020>Besides, this wasn't the first time Yu-san and I had waited to meet each other.

//TEXT
<jaT0021>We didn't care about the promise that it would only be one time. Yu-san and I had met for several rendezvous since then.
<enT0021>We didn't care about the promise that it would only be one time. Yu-san and I had met for several rendezvous since then.

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0022>"Ryota, do you have enough time? You have to stand up and address everyone, so shouldn't you get there early so you can be ready?"
<enT0022>"Ryota, do you have enough time? You have to stand up and address everyone, so shouldn't you get there early so you can be ready?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0023>"Hah... I hate speeches."
<enT0023>"Hah... I hate speeches."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0024>"Hehe... Do your best, Leader of the Sheratan."
<enT0024>"Hehe... Do your best, Leader of the Sheratan."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0025>"Why do you think it's someone else's affair... Besides, I'm your former leader. I'm not your leader anymore..."
<enT0025>"Why do you think it's someone else's affair... Besides, I'm your former leader. I'm not your leader anymore..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0026>"You're a man, so don't worry about the details. Anyways, do you really have enough time? By my watch, it's about time you went to the reception hall..."
<enT0026>"You're a man, so don't worry about the details. Anyways, do you really have enough time? By my watch, it's about time you went to the reception hall..."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0027>"Ohh... I-It is a little close..."
<enT0027>"Ohh... I-It is a little close..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0028>"Do your best. I'll be listening from the front row..."
<enT0028>"Do your best. I'll be listening from the front row..."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0029>"That just puts more pressure on me. Well, I'd be sad if you didn't listen though."
<enT0029>"That just puts more pressure on me. Well, I'd be sad if you didn't listen though."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0030>"Sheesh... Then what do you expect me to do?"
<enT0030>"Sheesh... Then what do you expect me to do?"

//TEXT
<jaT0031>Yu-san looked at me, frustrated.
<enT0031>Yu-san looked at me, frustrated.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0032>"Hahaha... Well, then how about you listen from the center seat instead of the front row?"
<enT0032>"Hahaha... Well, then how about you listen from the center seat instead of the front row?"

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0033>"Yes, yes, alright..."
<enT0033>"Yes, yes, alright..."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0034>"I'll see you later then!"
<enT0034>"I'll see you later then!"

//TEXT
<jaT0035>I waved my hand at Yu-san and ran towards the reception hall.
<enT0035>I waved my hand at Yu-san and ran towards the reception hall.

//TEXT
<jaT0036>......
<enT0036>......

//TEXT
<jaT0037>...
<enT0037>...

//TEXT
<jaT0038>After the ceremony ended, I returned to my previous spot for a breath of air.
<enT0038>After the ceremony ended, I returned to my previous spot for a breath of air.

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0039>"Ryota-kun, you can do it when you try. I don't really know that stuff, but you looked good up there."
<enT0039>"Ryota-kun, you can do it when you try. I don't really know that stuff, but you looked good up there."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0040>"Ehen, was I amazing?"
<enT0040>"Ehen, was I amazing?"

//TEXT
<jaT0041>As I held my head up proud, I took a small envelope out of my uniform pocket.
<enT0041>As I held my head up proud, I took a small envelope out of my uniform pocket.

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0042>"What's that envelope?"
<enT0042>"What's that envelope?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0043>"I don't know. It arrived this morning and on the back there was a woman's handwriting. It read, 'Please open this after the ceremony is over.'"
<enT0043>"I don't know. It arrived this morning and on the back there was a woman's handwriting. It read, 'Please open this after the ceremony is over.'"

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0044>"Ohh... That's a strange envelope."
<enT0044>"Ohh... That's a strange envelope."

//TEXT
<jaT0045>Yu-san tilted her head in curiosity.
<enT0045>Yu-san tilted her head in curiosity.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0046>"Maybe there's a reward inside for giving a good speech?"
<enT0046>"Maybe there's a reward inside for giving a good speech?"

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0047>"Hmm, I don't think that's case."
<enT0047>"Hmm, I don't think that's case."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0048>"Well, I'm not expecting anything... Or does my girlfriend, Yu-san, have any reward she wants to give me?"
<enT0048>"Well, I'm not expecting anything... Or does my girlfriend, Yu-san, have any reward she wants to give me?"

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0049>"Eh? A reward?"
<enT0049>"Eh? A reward?"

//TEXT
<jaT0050>Yu-san looked bewildered to hear my silly request.
<enT0050>Yu-san looked bewildered to hear my silly request.

//TEXT
<jaT0051>I was half joking, so I didn't mind if she ignored it, but one of her cute points was the way she took everything seriously. As I thought this to myself, I emphasized the word reward.
<enT0051>I was half joking, so I didn't mind if she ignored it, but one of her cute points was the way she took everything seriously. As I thought this to myself, I emphasized the word reward.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0052>"Yes, a reward. A reward for giving a good speech."
<enT0052>"Yes, a reward. A reward for giving a good speech."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0053>"I-If you ask me for that all of a sudden..."
<enT0053>"I-If you ask me for that all of a sudden..."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0054>"Anything is fine. It doesn't have to be an object, as long as it's something I can remember..."
<enT0054>"Anything is fine. It doesn't have to be an object, as long as it's something I can remember..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0055>"Hmm, well..."
<enT0055>"Hmm, well..."

//TEXT
<jaT0056>Yu-san crossed her arms in thought.
<enT0056>Yu-san crossed her arms in thought.

//TEXT
<jaT0057>After seriously pondering it for a while, she finally found her answer and spoke to me with a side glance.
<enT0057>After seriously pondering it for a while, she finally found her answer and spoke to me with a side glance.

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0058>"Then... can you close your eyes for a moment?"
<enT0058>"Then... can you close your eyes for a moment?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0059>"Yea, sure."
<enT0059>"Yea, sure."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0060>"......"
<enT0060>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0061>My heart was beating with excitement. What is she going to do?
<enT0061>My heart was beating with excitement. What is she going to do?

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0062>"Not yet?"
<enT0062>"Not yet?"

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0063>"Wait a little more... Okay, now you can."
<enT0063>"Wait a little more... Okay, now you can."

//TEXT
<jaT0064>When I opened my eyes...
<enT0064>When I opened my eyes...

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0065>"Wha, whah..."
<enT0065>"Wha, whah..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0066>"H-how is it?"
<enT0066>"H-how is it?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0067>"Great. It's really great. You're beautiful, Yu-san..."
<enT0067>"Great. It's really great. You're beautiful, Yu-san..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0068>"Thank you. I was actually wondering if it was about time for me to let my hair down..."
<enT0068>"Thank you. I was actually wondering if it was about time for me to let my hair down..."

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0069>"Today's the day it all came to an end, so I thought that maybe it was time."
<enT0069>"Today's the day it all came to an end, so I thought that maybe it was time."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0070>"......"
<enT0070>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0071>My heart swelled as I remembered that she said, "I don't let my hair down during missions," and, "This is the last time you'll see me with my hair down."
<enT0071>My heart swelled as I remembered that she said, "I don't let my hair down during missions," and, "This is the last time you'll see me with my hair down."

//TEXT
<jaT0072>To her, changing her hairstyle meant more than just a simple image change.
<enT0072>To her, changing her hairstyle meant more than just a simple image change.

//TEXT
<jaT0073>Her glossy, long hair meant that she threw away her life as a mercenary and has finally come to consider herself feminine enough to wear it like that.
<enT0073>Her glossy, long hair meant that she threw away her life as a mercenary and has finally come to consider herself feminine enough to wear it like that.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0074>"...From now on, you'll keep your hair down? Even on our dates too?"
<enT0074>"...From now on, you'll keep your hair down? Even on our dates too?"

//TEXT 【Yu】
<jaT0075>"Yes, that's my intention."
<enT0075>"Yes, that's my intention."

//TEXT
<jaT0076>Yu-san replied with a shy smile.
<enT0076>Yu-san replied with a shy smile.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0077>"(Thank you, Yu-san.)"
<enT0077>"(Thank you, Yu-san.)"

//TEXT
<jaT0078>I promise I'll make her happy. With that thought revived, I gently wrapped my arms around her...
<enT0078>I promise I'll make her happy. With that thought revived, I gently wrapped my arms around her...

//TEXT
<jaT0079>......
<enT0079>......

//TEXT
<jaT0080>...
<enT0080>...

